com.orm.androrm
Class Statement

java.lang.Object
  com.orm.androrm.Statement
Direct Known Subclasses:
ComposedStatement, InStatement, LikeStatement
public class Statement
extends Object

This class is the superclass of all statements. The whole statement structure is used to build up where complex Where clauses. The abstract grammar of a Statement is the following. 

   KEY   -> STRING
   VALUE -> STRING
   
   STMT -> KEY = 'VALUE'
   STMT -> LIKE_STMT
   STMT -> COMPOSED_STMT
   
   LIKE_STMT -> KEY LIKE '%VALUE%'
   
   COMPOSED_STMT -> AND_STMT
   COMPOSED_STMT -> OR_STMT
   
   AND_STMT -> STMT
   AND_STMT -> STMT AND STMT
   
   OR_STMT -> STMT
   OR_STMT -> STMT OR STMT

Author:
Philipp Giese
